{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/blog/gatsby-blog-with-netlify/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Tistory, 벨로그 등의 블로그 플랫폼을 이용하다가, 직접 커스텀해보고싶은 부분들이 있어서 GitHub Blog를 구축해보기로 했다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Gatsby</h2>\n<p><code>Gatsby</code>는 정적 사이트 생성기이다.<br>\nGitHub 블로그를 구축할 때 Ruby 기반의 <code>Jekyll</code>과 React 기반의 <code>Gatsby</code>가 주로 언급되는데,\n<del>그나마</del> React가 좀 더 친숙했기에 <code>Gatsby</code>를 선택했다.</p>\n<p><code>Gatsby</code>의 <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/docs/quick-start/\">Quick Start</a>를 따라하면 기초적인 블로그를 쉽게 만들 수 있다.<br>\n이 상태에서 UI/UX를 직접 설계하며 블로그를 개발하면 많은 것을 배울 수 있겠지만,<br>\n빠르게 블로그를 구축하고 싶고, 개발 및 학습 시간을 많이 투자하기 부담스럽다면 템플릿을 기반으로 구축하는 것도 좋다.<br>\n템플릿은 구글링하거나 GitHub에 검색하여 찾아볼 수 있다.</p>\n<p>필자는 디자인이 가장 마음에 드는 <a href=\"https://github.com/sungik-choi/gatsby-starter-apple\">gatsby-starter-apple</a>로 결정했다.<br>\n템플릿마다 구현이나 표현 방식에 차이가 있을 수 있음에 유의한다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Gatsby Repository 클론 및 로컬에서 실행하기</h2>\n<p>먼저, 기반이 되는 Repository를 <code>clone</code>한다.<br>\n<code>gatsby-cli</code> 패키지를 설치하면 <code>gatsby</code> 명령어를 사용할 수 있다.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container github-light-theme grvsc-ps-t4tStz\" data-language=\"shell\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">npm install -g gatsby-cli</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">gatsby new youseokhwan.me https://github.com/sungik-choi/gatsby-starter-apple</span></span></code></pre>\n<p><code>youseokhwan.me</code>는 로컬 디렉토리 이름, Github 주소는 <code>clone</code>할 Repository의 주소이다.<br>\n로컬 디렉토리 이름은 자유롭게 지어도 된다.<br></p>\n<p>필요한 모듈을 설치하면, 로컬에서 실행해볼 수 있다.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container github-light-theme grvsc-ps-t4tStz\" data-language=\"shell\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">cd youseokhwan.me</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">yarn install</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">gatsby develop</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>브라우저에 <a href=\"http://localhost:8000/\">http://localhost:8000/</a>을 입력하여 접속할 수 있고,<br>\nUI를 변경하거나, 포스트를 작성하면서 중간중간 결과물을 확인할 수 있다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>GitHub Repository 생성 및 remote 연결</h2>\n<p>GitHub에서 <code>youseokhwan.me</code> Repository를 생성한다.<br>\n이후, 로컬 디렉토리 <code>youseokhwan.me</code>와 이 Repository를 연결한다.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container github-light-theme grvsc-ps-t4tStz\" data-language=\"shell\" data-index=\"2\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">rm -rf .git</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">git init</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">git add .</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">git commit -m &quot;clone gatsby-starter-apple&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">git remote add origin https://github.com/youseokhwan/youseokhwan.me</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">git push -u origin main</span></span></code></pre>\n<hr>\n<h2>포스트 작성</h2>\n<p>포스트는 <code>src/posts/blog/</code> 경로에 마크다운 파일을 추가하는 방식으로 작성할 수 있다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 68.09815950920245%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"new_post.png\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/ca35f38da88a9c235ebc31ad5ade19e6/a6d36/new_post.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ca35f38da88a9c235ebc31ad5ade19e6/222b7/new_post.png 163w,\n/static/ca35f38da88a9c235ebc31ad5ade19e6/ff46a/new_post.png 325w,\n/static/ca35f38da88a9c235ebc31ad5ade19e6/a6d36/new_post.png 650w,\n/static/ca35f38da88a9c235ebc31ad5ade19e6/e548f/new_post.png 975w,\n/static/ca35f38da88a9c235ebc31ad5ade19e6/3c492/new_post.png 1300w,\n/static/ca35f38da88a9c235ebc31ad5ade19e6/f3c07/new_post.png 2516w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Netlify로 블로그 배포하기</h2>\n<p>현재는 로컬에서만 접속할 수 있고, 외부에서는 접속할 수 없는 상태이다.<br>\n외부에서 접속하려면 이 블로그를 배포(deploy)해야한다.</p>\n<p>정적 사이트를 쉽고 빠르게 배포해주는 <a href=\"https://www.netlify.com/\">Netlify</a>를 통해 블로그를 배포할 것이다.<br>\n회원 가입을 하고 <code>youseokhwan.me</code> Repository를 등록한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 65.03067484662577%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"netlify_01.png\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/892d6a709775d74da246f0a92e428e09/a6d36/netlify_01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/892d6a709775d74da246f0a92e428e09/222b7/netlify_01.png 163w,\n/static/892d6a709775d74da246f0a92e428e09/ff46a/netlify_01.png 325w,\n/static/892d6a709775d74da246f0a92e428e09/a6d36/netlify_01.png 650w,\n/static/892d6a709775d74da246f0a92e428e09/e548f/netlify_01.png 975w,\n/static/892d6a709775d74da246f0a92e428e09/3c492/netlify_01.png 1300w,\n/static/892d6a709775d74da246f0a92e428e09/669cd/netlify_01.png 3024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Build settings은 다음과 같이 입력했다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Build command: <code>gatsby build</code></li>\n<li>Publish directory: <code>public</code></li>\n<li>나머지는 빈칸으로 두거나 그대로 유지</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 65.03067484662577%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"netlify_02.png\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/33773001e0885d7dd76da1494357b735/a6d36/netlify_02.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/33773001e0885d7dd76da1494357b735/222b7/netlify_02.png 163w,\n/static/33773001e0885d7dd76da1494357b735/ff46a/netlify_02.png 325w,\n/static/33773001e0885d7dd76da1494357b735/a6d36/netlify_02.png 650w,\n/static/33773001e0885d7dd76da1494357b735/e548f/netlify_02.png 975w,\n/static/33773001e0885d7dd76da1494357b735/3c492/netlify_02.png 1300w,\n/static/33773001e0885d7dd76da1494357b735/669cd/netlify_02.png 3024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>브랜치는 우선 <code>main</code>으로 설정했다.<br>\n<code>main</code>을 배포 브랜치로 바로 사용하는 것에 대한 거부감이 있지만, CI/CD 개선은 추후에 하기로 하고 우선 진행했다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 65.03067484662577%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"netlify_03.png\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/f5142734ca88ad9460f528d145309068/a6d36/netlify_03.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f5142734ca88ad9460f528d145309068/222b7/netlify_03.png 163w,\n/static/f5142734ca88ad9460f528d145309068/ff46a/netlify_03.png 325w,\n/static/f5142734ca88ad9460f528d145309068/a6d36/netlify_03.png 650w,\n/static/f5142734ca88ad9460f528d145309068/e548f/netlify_03.png 975w,\n/static/f5142734ca88ad9460f528d145309068/3c492/netlify_03.png 1300w,\n/static/f5142734ca88ad9460f528d145309068/669cd/netlify_03.png 3024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>도메인은 <code>{사이트 이름}.netlify.app</code>으로 결정된다.<br>\n필자의 경우 <a href=\"https://youseokhwan.netlify.app\">youseokhwan.netlify.app</a>이 된다.\n<code>Site configuration</code>에서 변경할 수 있다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.44171779141104%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"netlify_04.png\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d33093c4bfc49fc2a4ddfbc177622263/a6d36/netlify_04.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d33093c4bfc49fc2a4ddfbc177622263/222b7/netlify_04.png 163w,\n/static/d33093c4bfc49fc2a4ddfbc177622263/ff46a/netlify_04.png 325w,\n/static/d33093c4bfc49fc2a4ddfbc177622263/a6d36/netlify_04.png 650w,\n/static/d33093c4bfc49fc2a4ddfbc177622263/e548f/netlify_04.png 975w,\n/static/d33093c4bfc49fc2a4ddfbc177622263/8d68c/netlify_04.png 1234w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>이제 Repository의 변경 사항이 감지되면 Netlify가 자동으로 배포한다.<br>\n배포 과정이나 로그는 <code>Deploys</code> 탭에서 확인할 수 있다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>커스텀 도메인 연결</h2>\n<p>가지고 있는 도메인이 있다면 연결할 수 있다.<br>\n가비아에서 구매한 <code>youseokhwan.me</code>라는 도메인을 이 블로그와 연결하였다.</p>\n<p>먼저, 가비아에서 DNS를 다음과 같이 설정했다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30.67484662576687%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"custom_domain_01.png\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/421e1f66fb061f0f34c44bc48ea8320e/a6d36/custom_domain_01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/421e1f66fb061f0f34c44bc48ea8320e/222b7/custom_domain_01.png 163w,\n/static/421e1f66fb061f0f34c44bc48ea8320e/ff46a/custom_domain_01.png 325w,\n/static/421e1f66fb061f0f34c44bc48ea8320e/a6d36/custom_domain_01.png 650w,\n/static/421e1f66fb061f0f34c44bc48ea8320e/e548f/custom_domain_01.png 975w,\n/static/421e1f66fb061f0f34c44bc48ea8320e/3c492/custom_domain_01.png 1300w,\n/static/421e1f66fb061f0f34c44bc48ea8320e/88745/custom_domain_01.png 2148w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><code>104.198.14.52</code>는 Netlify에서 제공하는 A 레코드 IP주소이다.<br>\nCNAME 설정은 <code>www.youseokhwan.me</code>를 <code>youseokhwan.netlify.app</code>으로 리다이렉트하는 역할을 한다.</p>\n<p>이후, Netlify 설정의 Domain management 탭에서 구매한 도메인을 추가해준다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.920245398773%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"custom_domain_02.png\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/12f301aaf0fd2dbe7fac158187b9a276/a6d36/custom_domain_02.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/12f301aaf0fd2dbe7fac158187b9a276/222b7/custom_domain_02.png 163w,\n/static/12f301aaf0fd2dbe7fac158187b9a276/ff46a/custom_domain_02.png 325w,\n/static/12f301aaf0fd2dbe7fac158187b9a276/a6d36/custom_domain_02.png 650w,\n/static/12f301aaf0fd2dbe7fac158187b9a276/e548f/custom_domain_02.png 975w,\n/static/12f301aaf0fd2dbe7fac158187b9a276/3c492/custom_domain_02.png 1300w,\n/static/12f301aaf0fd2dbe7fac158187b9a276/9efb3/custom_domain_02.png 1894w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>바로 밑 HTTPS 항목의 <code>Verify DNS Configuration</code>을 클릭하면 Netlify가 설정된 DNS 레코드를 검사한다.<br>\nDNS가 올바르게 설정되었다면 자동으로 <code>Let's Encrypt SSL</code> 인증서를 발급하여 HTTPS를 활성화 시켜준다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 69.32515337423312%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"custom_domain_03.png\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/fb28f6021c4f121d534cc4ee67bf74f2/a6d36/custom_domain_03.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fb28f6021c4f121d534cc4ee67bf74f2/222b7/custom_domain_03.png 163w,\n/static/fb28f6021c4f121d534cc4ee67bf74f2/ff46a/custom_domain_03.png 325w,\n/static/fb28f6021c4f121d534cc4ee67bf74f2/a6d36/custom_domain_03.png 650w,\n/static/fb28f6021c4f121d534cc4ee67bf74f2/e548f/custom_domain_03.png 975w,\n/static/fb28f6021c4f121d534cc4ee67bf74f2/3c492/custom_domain_03.png 1300w,\n/static/fb28f6021c4f121d534cc4ee67bf74f2/0e0c4/custom_domain_03.png 1884w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>잠시 기다려주면 <a href=\"https://youseokhwan.me\">https://youseokhwan.me</a>로 잘 접속되는 것을 확인할 수 있다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 67.48466257668711%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"custom_domain_04.png\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/2f5c31afc787172d49549a321c8a1767/a6d36/custom_domain_04.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2f5c31afc787172d49549a321c8a1767/222b7/custom_domain_04.png 163w,\n/static/2f5c31afc787172d49549a321c8a1767/ff46a/custom_domain_04.png 325w,\n/static/2f5c31afc787172d49549a321c8a1767/a6d36/custom_domain_04.png 650w,\n/static/2f5c31afc787172d49549a321c8a1767/e548f/custom_domain_04.png 975w,